window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>A witch and a Vampire Prince, bound by a dark past and forbidden desire, must unite to uncover deadly secrets before their connection destroys them.</i></b><br> <br> He steps out of the shadows, sending a chill straight through my soul. Eyes the deepest shade of amethyst pierced mine. His cold, handsome features tell me everything I need to know—vampire.<br> <br> But Gabriel de Montclair is not just any vampire. He’s the ancient Vampire Prince.<br> Like me, he’s looking for something. I’m a paranormal investigator searching for a powerful supernatural artifact, and he’s investigating a series of mysterious disappearances among the vampire clans.<br> <br> I could never trust him, but if I agree to help him, he will aid me in finding answers about my unknown past and unique witchcraft. But as we grapple to survive the deadly forces conspiring against me, I learn that I’m not the only one haunted by a dark past.<br> <br> It seems our fates have been intertwined since the beginning, and the dangerous, forbidden desire sparking between us has the power to destroy everything…<br> <br> <i>Soulbound Shadows is a paranormal adventure romance with a quick-witted FMC that will have you considering a career as a PI, and a sexy but slightly nerdy MC who’ll have you wanting your own life and death hunt for a relic with a vampire.<br> <br> This is part 1 of a duet and will end on a cliffhanger.</i></p>"; 
